HEADWORD: Exesion
<hw>Ex*e"sion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>exedere</ets>, <ets>exesum</ets>, to eat up; <ets>ex</ets> out +
<ets>edere</ets> to eat.]</ety> <def>The act of eating out or
through.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Sir T. Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
